 Shola Ogudu and Her Boyfriend Shola Ogudu has finally shown off her boyfriend, fitness consultant Razzie. Shola sharing the photos of her and her boyfriend wrote; “If Happiness, Love, Peace and Joy were HUMANS ? SMILE JESUS LOVES YOU ?” According to rumors, Shola and Razzie are engaged and are set to tie the knot soon. Shola after her relationship with Wizkid hasn’t been in any public relationship but is now out of the singles group after showing off her fiance publicly. https://twitter.com/oluwanishola/status/1352230244418269185?s=21